                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">背靠大树真的好乘凉么？ ——环雅博德由加盟到自营的雅思培训之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Anything to fall back on?---Huanya Bode’s road to IELTS from a Franchisee to Self-operated business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张静</td>
