                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雅思；特许经营；品牌；核心竞争力；战略决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IELTS;Franchising;Brand;Core competence;Strategic decision</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以雅思考试培训为核心，南京环雅博德教育培训中心从事出国英语和系列国际证书培训、相关图书出版，留学移民咨询服务等业务，旨在通过创新性的教育理念和资源整合方式，为考生提供一体化的解决方案。伴随着雅思考试市场的变化，环雅博德经历了由加盟到独立运作的发展历程。进入自营发展的另一个阶段，公司面临着由被特许方到特许方的角色转变，在线上教育的冲击下，如何进一步整合企业内外部资源，通过市场聚焦构建可持续的竞争力？环雅博德面临重大抉择。案例旨在启发学生对动态环境下，企业不断创新以培育核心竞争力的过程进行深入思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With a series of business from English test training, book publishing, overseas study services, Nanjing Huanya Bode Education is devoted to providing value-added solutions for students going abroad. Along with the dramatic changes in IELTS test market in China, it develops from a franchisee of original Global IELTS to independent operation. Huanya Bode Education is entering a new stage of development by changing from a franchisee to franchiser. Facing the impact of on-line education technologies, can it find new opportunities by leveraging on a specific market with resource integration? The company comes to the big decisions. This case inspires students to think deeply about how innovation has always been put in the first place to nurture the core competence in dynamic environments.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
